					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5979143#post-4647535</guid>
				<title>My favorite reference in SCP Canon to date</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5979143/scp-3768#post-4647535</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2020 06:57:20 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Cupper_Nick</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5858552</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>&quot;I've been bloody well disappointed the whole time. There I was, all &quot;imagine there's no heaven&quot; and &quot;no hell below us&quot; - then I wake up from the murder, and I'm in a place that manages to be both at the same time.&quot;</p> </blockquote> <p>Enough for me to upvote. Great SCP</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
