					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5979143#post-3807518</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5979143/scp-3768#post-3807518</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 21 May 2018 13:22:31 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>CalamityHeart</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1973848</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>When this happens - and it has happened, all too often - the polarity of death is reversed, and the departed mortal leaves to live forever in Corbenic's so-called &quot;sister universe&quot;.</p> <p>The tricky bit with this, of course, is that our world is designed for immortals. Theirs isn't.</p> </blockquote> <p>Hard upvote.</p> <p>I love Corbenic, and I love the implications of this particular line.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
